content: परिच्यु {c1c} <ab>A.</ab> {@--1@} To go away or fly off from, escape. {@--2@} To proceed from. {@--3@} To swerve, fall off from, deviate, leave. {@--4@} To lose. be deprived of, {@--5@} To drop or fall down. {@--6@} To be displaced or ejected from. {@--7@} To be freed from. {@--8@} To come down, descend.
